{"type": "article", "id": 2277, "title": "复古陶瓷灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-10T01:22:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222330x5lmi6gMzaUkWnyq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国家具品牌 Another Country 邀请加拿大设计师 Dana Cannam 为其设计了一款灯饰 First Light ，灵感来自于 20 世纪的手工工具。这款灯饰用的是手工制作的圆柱陶瓷灯罩，金属部分用的是黄铜材质。设计师认为陶瓷和黄铜的搭配，显得复古又典雅，造型简洁，细节上借由黄铜让整体显得不那么单调。First Light 目前正在巴黎举行的 <a href=\"http://www.maison-objet.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">Maison &amp; Objet 贸易展览会</a>上展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222328C18Jr2EU0j4SLfuK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"http://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0048/4002/files/another-country-first-light-newsletter_grande.gif?7254\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222329XcoWmAV9z0i7tg3C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222329x7dw3BXrWHpcTUPf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}